        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nrenaming and/or changing the blueprints for k8s is outside of the scope of this change.  \nThat should be done in accord with the code that consumes the blueprint yaml files as a separate user story when it is ready.  \n\nThis change is only to have the latest versions of deployment-handler + policy-handler plus the new config for policy-handler catch_up logic",
